'''Soun-Giju''' was a [[Herglic/Legends|Herglic]] settlement on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Tallaan]]. It maintained the culture of [[Giju/Legends|Giju]] rather than melding with its neighboring [[Human/Legends|Human]] culture. Its name translated to "Little Giju".<ref name="LE">''[[Lords of the Expanse]]''</ref>

